121
00:11:58,519 --> 00:11:59,919
Please forgive us.

122
00:12:08,159 --> 00:12:08,799
And also,

123
00:12:09,759 --> 00:12:11,919
let us borrow

124
00:12:12,559 --> 00:12:14,000
the ginseng gang's outfits.

125
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:17,519
