128
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:26,519
Thank you, thank you, thank you.

129
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:30,799
Lao Batou

130
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,919
Everything you told us

131
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,000
