138
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,320
Go to sleep.

139
00:14:25,679 --> 00:14:26,639
Unlucky guy.

140
00:14:29,399 --> 00:14:30,320
Take him away.

141
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:35,919
No one admits who did the killing.

142
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:36,519
Right?

143
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:48,559
The ones who stirred up trouble a few days ago,

144
00:14:49,159 --> 00:14:50,799
