157
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:55,080
Each of you, pick one.

158
00:15:56,919 --> 00:15:59,879
Let’s have an intimate showdown.

159
00:16:00,759 --> 00:16:01,480
The rule is,

160
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:03,519
