163
00:16:12,440 --> 00:16:13,440
Three, two, one.

164
00:16:18,159 --> 00:16:19,480
Aren’t you starting yet?

165
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:20,720
If you don’t start,

166
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:22,960
all Koreans

167
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:24,639
die.

168
00:16:58,679 --> 00:16:59,519
I think

169
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:02,759
