170
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:19,200
Push me harder.

171
00:17:20,359 --> 00:17:21,079
Push me harder.

172
00:17:21,599 --> 00:17:22,200
Hurry up.

173
00:17:55,279 --> 00:17:56,160
Brilliant.

174
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:58,400
That was truly brilliant.

175
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:02,960
Victory.

176
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:04,279
Congratulations.

177
00:18:08,799 --> 00:18:09,960
Absolutely brilliant.

178
00:18:11,039 --> 00:18:11,640
From now on,

179
00:18:12,359 --> 00:18:14,720
everyone should get along peacefully.

180
00:18:15,599 --> 00:18:16,279
Remember,

181
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:18,200
the only reason you can stay here

182
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:19,799
