198
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:45,960
Those two scallions?

199
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:47,519
Just these two scallions

200
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:48,880
They've got some skills

201
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:50,680
Skills

202
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:52,359
What about it?

203
00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:54,839
Can they fly?

204
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:56,519
Or dig underground?

205
00:21:00,119 --> 00:21:00,640
Come on

206
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:02,240
Let me have a look too

207
00:21:08,039 --> 00:21:08,920
