Everyone, come out

227
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:42,039
Hand it over, hand it over.

228
00:22:42,039 --> 00:22:43,200
Go away.

229
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:46,319
Didn't expect you

230
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:48,039
