288
00:25:36,279 --> 00:25:37,160
and our ginseng crew.

289
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:42,359
We have to endure it.

290
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:47,559
Eat more, eat up.

291
00:25:48,039 --> 00:25:50,400
Don't let your body give out.

292
00:25:56,000 --> 00:25:56,359
Thanks.

293
00:25:59,759 --> 00:26:00,920
